ón exhaustiva\\Ndel dolor, la función y el contenido psicosocial.","guid":"qkgEp6V0cAYbhW-SC5WkTw","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"47","text":"Dolor generalizado","guid":"_LlNaD3-wtl_ouQ_8le3Qw","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"AM 2/3 de los casos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"47","text":"Parestesias sin causa neurologica","guid":"kHjd5rAaNGBhdHvHT2u49g","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"47","text":"Rigidez matinal menor a 15 minutos","guid":"0AhEoGzj2Czdywm5uTXp-g","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"47","text":"Asociación a disfunción ATM","guid":"aIIFrAcLMhFcCq3QpkDjvg","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"47","text":"Hipersensibilidad a sonido","guid":"G58DxoR7Oa6a7fNglgSrXQ","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"47","text":"Alteración del sueño","guid":"f3aYqQBc-vyEuIMQ0M45gw","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"47","text":"Síndrome SICA","guid":"hyj5QR88o79QHQAI07SSMg","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"47","text":"En AM\\Nconsiderar","guid":"aK1Iq9lsXeRF4nrx4b8fZg","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"Puede persistir por muchos años sin diagnostico","guid":"V01fyRmD_TI2RNuEih7X3g","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"Puede aparecer de novio en AM","guid":"5GGiY4M9x7RYay0-ur_Awg","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"Dolor generalizado puede estar dado no por fibromialgia","guid":"qi5awpaPoXwHpJwQHCIElw","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"60","text":"Puede atribuirse a otras patologías concomitantes","guid":"cOpxOp1VHRq4IHIGr7ruXg","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"47","text":"Examen fisico","guid":"7rE_6AOyFjy9kQJtiZ3G8A","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"Puntos de gatillo\\NS/E. Variable","guid":"MteQPs4Vzs8CTHwGmMCaEQ","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"En desuso","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"Diagnostico diferencial","guid":"nkdMsJDKytoEZRLtqtcIUg","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"47","text":"Criterios","guid":"1NPw8qrQuR1xb7OzyJ047Q